OL,3,CRevised pay offer suspends bus strike
OL,4,Cin Northumberland
OL,6,FA planned bus strike in Northumberland
OL,7,Fhas been suspended after the union
OL,8,Fagreed to put a new pay offer to
OL,9,Fmembers.
OL,11,FMore than 300 drivers and engineers at
OL,12,FArriva's depots in Blyth and Ashington
OL,13,Fhad voted to go on strike later this
OL,14,Fmonth.
OL,16,FArriva North East confirmed that
OL,17,Fmembers of Unite the Union have agreed
OL,18,Fto take the revised pay offer to their
OL,19,Fmembers and to suspend the industrial
OL,20,Faction planned from 7-13 April.
